Singe / Performer: MC Stan ( Official baap )
Music Composer: MC Stan 
Author / Lyrics: MC Stan
Prod. by MC STŒîN



  LYRICS :   
              
                      ‚Äú HOOK ‚Äú

Chodna kam chillana jyada , Mein basti ka hasti 
mein malum kya kider se aata ,  P town baby 
Mein tumlog ko accha seekharela , bhai aane do peti
Yeh lund k bal , mere samne banra braZy

Mein basti ka , hasti bro 
Agyele bhai log , abhi kalti lo
Maine bombay mei bachaya ek , bacchi ko
Ider fire hogayeli dekh , palti bro

Mein basti ka , hasti broo
Amir mein hogayela , gareeb hai flow
Represent karta mein , basti ko
Yeh bhadwe karele nakli , show

                 ( VERSE - 1 )

Mein rapper nai , gangster hai 
Tu rapper nai , dancer hai
Acting tu karela rawas ha par , tu shyad se actor hai
Mein janeka  , dost log k matter mei 

Teku Marneka maan bhi nai karela  , sadela cancer hai tu 
Teko isleye mei leke nai jata bro kider bhi , kyuki bro phachad hai tu 

Yeh shemde ku batare ,
Apun kider se aare ann kider ko jaare 
Yeh basti mei pakare ,
Yeh lund k baal ku , lund pr mare

Aaj stannyy bole phakat hai ,
Leke jayega teku , mein bhaga k 
Tere baju wale , mere gaane bajate
Meko malum na , ed kaise bhagate
 phakat hai !

Mein actor ka ladka nai , aayela mei basti se 
meko bolte basti ka hasti
Mein gareebi se aayela bro , bombae ki public meko bolneki jande bacchi

Mere gaano pe , agar haat nai varti
Mere shows pe nai , badach ki gardi
Meri malum na , kider pan chalti 
Mere dost log ki gand, kaiku jaltiiiiiiiiiiiii ?

                      ‚Äú HOOK ‚Äú

Chodna kam chillana jyada , Mein basti ka hasti 
mein malum kya kider se aata , P town baby 
Mein tumlog ko accha seekharela , bhai aane de peti
Yeh lund k bal , mere samne banra braZy

Mein basti ka , hasti bro 
Agyele bhai log , abhi kalti lo
Maine bombay mei bachaya ek , bacchi ko
Ider fire hogayeli dekh , palti bro

Mein basti ka , hasti broo
Amir mein hogayela , gareeb hai flow
Represent karta mein , basti ko
Yeh bhadwe karele nakli , show

               ( VERSE  - 2 )

Maine Bola khudko , altaf shaikh 
Tu tera dekh , wer is ma shades 
Wer is ma js , now these days
uh heard ma name , fuck dat fame 
use ur brain , stay in ur lane
Apun dono same
Nobody knows ma , pain 
Mein bolrela sach , mere sach se bach

Mein bolrela hindi ( Hindi )
Meri shawty jab , lagati bindi 
Meko goli nai , khaneka neend ki
Mein club mei jab , karela entry

Jaise saxxhi mei , horeli entry
Mein jhaad pe kabhi , chatda nai panchi 
Tera 3 din jalayega , one piece 
Maine ghar dikhaya , woch meri galti

Tune chowki mei , kha dali palti

Tumko gand dhone aaneki nai ,  tabhi se karra mein rap

Mein derela , slatt 
Mera vishye , no cap 

Tere japt kara , flat 
Teri japt kara , soch
Phele mere tak , poch 
Yeh randa sab bolrele , video mei lo
Mein phugri mei , bajta nai bro
Aai jhaun tak mitra mandal bro 
uh know !


                     ‚Äú HOOK ‚Äú

Chodna kam chillana jyada , Mein basti ka hasti 
mein malum na kider se aata ,  P town baby 
Mein tumlog ko accha seekhrela , bhai aane do peti
Yeh lund k bal , mere samne banra braZy

Mein basti ka , hasti bro 
Agyele bhai log , abhi kalti lo
Maine bombay mei bachaya ek , bacchi ko
Ider fire hogayeli dekh , palti bro

Mein basti ka , hasti broo
Amir mei hogayela  , gareeb hai flow

Aake baithte pairon mein
Choti choti baatein hoti

Dopehron mein*
Choti choti baatein hoti
Rehti hain bade shehron mein
Tu baith ton sahi bolero mein

Minister lagte ho babbu itna na tamjham karo*
Dar lagta hai duniya se ab itna bhi na naam karo*
Minister lagte ho elvish itna na tamjham karo*
Dar lagta hai duniya se ab itna bhi na naam karo*
Bas abhi to charche hote hain
Kuch apno mein kuch gairon mein
Choti choti baatein hoti
Rehti hain bade shehron mein
Tu baith ton sahi bolero mein

snippet.title: TVF Aspirants - Season 2 | Official Trailer | Streaming from 25 Oct On Amazon Prime Video
snippet.description:
Get ready for the highly anticipated return of Aspirants as they continue to take us on a rollercoaster ride of friendship, dreams, and dilemmas. As we witness the mentorship dynamic between Sandeep Bhaiya and Abhilash evolve, we're left with questions about how they'll manage their professional responsibilities alongside their deep friendship. 

From Rajinder Nagar to Rampur, this season takes our aspirants into the world of adulthood, testing their decisions in the face of life's challenges. Drama, laughter, and a whirlwind of emotions await you in this season.

#AspirantsOnPrime , new season 25th October!

Recap Aspirants Season 1 here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTB0eCoUXErY_KvRNKOERQtYSDPjOb8jw&si=TaG8xWK8ZrQEEjFD

Director: Apoorv Singh Karki

Producer: Arunabh Kumar
Executive Producers: Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey
Cast: Naveen Kasturia, Sunny Hinduja, Abhilash Thapliyal, Shivankit Parihar, Namita Dubey

Get ready for the highly anticipated return of Aspirants as they continue to take us on a rollercoaster ride of friendship, dreams, and dilemmas. As we witness the mentorship dynamic between Sandeep Bhaiya and Abhilash evolve, we're left with questions about how they'll manage their professional responsibilities alongside their deep friendship. 

From Rajinder Nagar to Rampur, this season takes our aspirants into the world of adulthood, testing their decisions in the face of life's challenges. Drama, laughter, and a whirlwind of emotions await you in this season.

#AspirantsOnPrime , new season 25th October!

Recap Aspirants Season 1 here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTB0eCoUXErY_KvRNKOERQtYSDPjOb8jw&si=TaG8xWK8ZrQEEjFD

Episode 3908: Ziddi Box
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide has wrapped himself with a blanket to avoid spilling food or tea since he is wearing a new kurta to fulfill an order. Madhavi is eager to see his new kurta, but Bhide is apprehensive about showing it off. Madhavi becomes agitated and tries to pull a trick on him with his tea. Bhide eventually removes the cover, and Madhavi is surprised by his appearance. Popatlal received a massive steel container from the marriage after finishing his ten-year membership, but he is unable to open it. All of the Gokuldham men try and fail to unlock it. What's inside the container?

Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ‚Çπ1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing.

Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination ‚Äì Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent ‚Äì no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting‚ÄØprimevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Kisi bhi ladai mein insaan ki aadhi jeet tabhi ho jati hai jab vo ladne ki himmat juta le. Student Shiv ko uske papa ne ghar se nikaal diya hai aur ab vo aa gaya hai Mukherjee Nagar ke warzone mein, jahan sapne bante bhi hai aur bigadte bhi. Dosari taraf SSC sir ke best teacher ko Khanna hijack kar leta hai aur us par ilzaam bhi lagata hai. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.description:

Episode 3907: Shiny Dandiya Sticks
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal believes his home is haunted as he runs for his life and asks Bapuji to hide in his room. Jethalal sees Tapu's glow-in-the-dark dandiya sticks as Tapu and Bapuji are playing with the neon dandiya sticks which haunts Jetha, but Jetha also believes these can be dangerous. Later, after overhearing Bagha and Bawri's chat, Jethalal chastises them as he is told that Bagha has gone to visit a doctor. Watch the episode.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3907, 20 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
